The '''''Maledoth''''' was a former [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[slaveship]] used in the [[Ramoan]] [[Ramoan relocation project|relocation project]] by the [[New Jedi Order|Jedi]]. According to [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]], the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] in control of the project was the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Lowbacca]]; when [[Gender/Legends|he]] left for the [[Unknown Regions/Legends|Unknown Regions]] the project came to a standstill because no others possessed his understanding of Yuuzhan Vong [[biot]]echnology.<ref name="Joiner King" />

